  <p>The community groups feature is the ability for a sub-community to be dynamically created within a community site by authorized users from the publish and author environments.</p> 
  <p>As of Communities <a href="../../communities/using/deploy-communities.md#latestfeaturepack">feature pack 1</a>, it is possible for groups to be nested within other groups</p> 
